.
          CALL       RSOPSCR1          * Positional Read
.
SHOW1000  CALL       RKOPSCR1          * Subsequent Read
          BRANCH     OVRCD,SHOW9999
.
          PACK      XXS,X30,X30,X30,X30
.
          MATCH      OPSCKEY,PROGKEY
.
          GOTO       SHOW9999 IF NOT EQUAL
.
