          DISPLAY   *POPSCDCOL:OPSCDROW,*V2LON,DOPSCFLD,*HOFF,". ",*+,OPSCDESC:
                    *POPSCKCOL:OPSCKROW,*+,XXS
.
          RESET     XXS
.
